    public static class ConfiguringGLRuntimeCapabilities.MyGLAutoDrawable
extends WorldWindowGLAutoDrawable
    Subclass of WorldWindowGLAutoDrawable which overrides the method WorldWindowGLAutoDrawable.init(com.jogamp.opengl.GLAutoDrawable) to configure the OpenGL features used by the WorldWind SDK.
